##################################################
#
#    README for Genbank dir
#
##################################################

------------------------
OBJECTIVE
-------------------------

  Use GenBank daily update to update the accession number information 
in ZFIN.

-------------------------
EXECUTION
--------------------------

   To run:	% gmake run

   This will be automated run every night by cron job. 

----------------------------
PROCEDURE
----------------------------
    
    gbaccession.pl guides the process. 
    By default, it downloads today's update file from ftp://ftp.ncbi.nih.gov/genbank/daily-nc. Or a specific date could be given in a format of MMDD as parameter. After unzip, the file is parsed by parseDaily.pl, generating nc_zf_acc.unl and a set of fasta files for BLAST db update. The nc_zf_acc.unl is used to update accession_bank and db_link tables by dailyUpdate.sql, and the fasta files are then passed on to embryonix/zygotix.
  